Package: COSERO
Type: Package
Title: R Interface and Shiny Application for the COSERO Hydrological Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mathew", "Herrnegger",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mathew.herrnegger@boku.ac.at"),
    person("COSERO development team",
           role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides a R interface for the COSERO hydrological model,
    including automated model execution, fast output reading, interactive Shiny
    visualization app, and Sobol-based global sensitivity analysis framework.
    Users can run COSERO simulations programmatically or through a web GUI.
